OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA chief fire officer took his own life
OL,8,Fbecause he just "couldn't take it
OL,9,Fanymore" after months of alleged
OL,10,Fharassment, his partner has told an
OL,11,Finquest.
OL,13,FWayne Brown, 54, chief fire officer at
OL,14,FWest Midlands Fire Service (WMFS), was
OL,15,Ffound at his flat in Birmingham by
OL,16,Fpolice on the morning of January 24
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,19,FColleagues alerted the police that he
OL,20,Fhad failed to turn up for work,
OL,21,FBirmingham Coroners' Court was told.
