OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Brown, the UK's first black fire
OL,8,Fchief, had been under pressure because
OL,9,Fof a "barrage" of harassment and
OL,10,Fcomplaints about his character in the
OL,11,Fform of emails, Freedom of Information
OL,12,Frequests and letters to his workplace.
OL,14,FThere were also social media posts
OL,15,Fmaking allegations about him.
OL,17,FHe had left a note for police saying
OL,18,Fthe last 18 months of his life had
OL,19,Fbeen "absolutely awful" and "I can't
OL,20,Fdo this anymore".
