OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr Brown's partner, Nicola White, told
OL,8,Fthe inquest on Monday that national
OL,9,Fmedia attention in relation to claims
OL,10,Fhe had lied on his CV and his LinkedIn
OL,11,Fpage about having an MBA postgraduate
OL,12,Fbusiness qualification ` which was a
OL,13,Frequirement for chief fire officers `
OL,14,Fwas the "final straw".
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@UO]
