OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court was told that on January 16
OL,8,Flast year, days before he took his own
OL,9,Flife, his colleagues had been copied
OL,10,Finto an email saying Mr Brown did not
OL,11,Fhave the MBA qualification from London
OL,12,FSouth Bank University he claimed to,
OL,13,Fwhich sparked an internal
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,FSatinder Sahota, monitoring officer
OL,17,Ffor WMFS, said after questioning him
OL,18,Fabout the claims, Mr Brown admitted he
OL,19,Fhad started an MBA but had not
OL,20,Ffinished it and apologised for putting
OL,21,Fit on his CV.
