OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs White said her partner was clearly
OL,8,F"low" about the ongoing investigation,
OL,9,Fbut felt the "final straw" for him was
OL,10,Fwhen a national news outlet ran a
OL,11,Fstory about him the night before he
OL,12,Ftook his own life.
OL,14,FShe said: "He just couldn't take it
OL,15,Fanymore. I said 'Wayne, you need to
OL,16,Fspeak to someone', but he didn't like
OL,17,Fto show his weaknesses.
