OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"He was the first person to support
OL,8,Fothers and tell them to seek help, but
OL,9,Fhe felt he needed to be strong for
OL,10,Feveryone else.
OL,12,F"On the Tuesday... I did think to ask
OL,13,Fhim, 'you're not going to do anything
OL,14,Fsilly are you?' but I put that thought
OL,15,Fimmediately out of my head because I
OL,16,Fthought he would never do that."
