OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDeputy chief fire officer Joanne
OL,8,FBowcock said in a statement read out
OL,9,Fat the inquest that she recognised Mr
OL,10,FBrown was under pressure due to the
OL,11,Falleged harassment and the media
OL,12,Finterest, but that she never
OL,13,Fconsidered he would take his own life.
OL,15,FShe said he appeared to be coping well
OL,16,Fbut when speaking to him on January 18
OL,17,Fafter the email about the MBA had been
OL,18,Freceived, told her he had "the worst
OL,19,Ftwo weeks of his life" and feared he
OL,20,Fwould be suspended.
