OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Jonathan
OL,8,FKiteley, who was the West Midlands
OL,9,FPolice officer investigating the
OL,10,Falleged harassment, said a man was
OL,11,Fcharged with harassing the fire chief
OL,12,Fin July 2023 and while there had been
OL,13,Fsome early court appearances, Mr Brown
OL,14,Fhad expressed "frustration" to DCI
OL,15,FKiteley that a court date had been
OL,16,Fpushed back.
OL,18,FHe said: "I had no idea he would go on
OL,19,Fto take his own life but I could tell
OL,20,Fthe constant barrage of contact was
OL,21,Fgetting to him.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@[O]zD@JOU
