OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"I appreciated it was difficult for
OL,8,Fhim to go on with his day job because
OL,9,Fof other pressures."
OL,11,FThe charges against the man accused of
OL,12,Fharassment were dropped by the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service after Mr Brown's
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FSenior coroner Louise Hunt, who
OL,17,Fpresided over the inquest, said Mr
OL,18,FBrown had died as a result of suicide
OL,19,Fand indicated she would be writing a
OL,20,FPrevention of Future Deaths report to
OL,21,FWMFS to raise concerns.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@TO]
