OL,3,CFire chief took own life amid probe
OL,4,Cinto claims he lied on his CV, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe said the fire service did not
OL,8,Fundertake any investigation following
OL,9,FMr Brown's death so lessons could be
OL,10,Flearned and was concerned that there
OL,11,Fwas no policy requiring them to do so.
OL,13,FMrs Hunt was also concerned there
OL,14,Fappeared to be no mechanism for
OL,15,Frecording concerns raised about the
OL,16,Fwelfare of staff during a fact-finding
OL,17,For formal investigation, and that
OL,18,Fthere was no provision in the
OL,19,Fservice's health and wellbeing or
OL,20,Fmental health policy for employees as
OL,21,Fsenior as Mr Brown was.
