OL,7,FIn a tribute, Mr Brown's son Kai said
OL,8,Fhe was "loved and respected", had many
OL,9,Ffriends and was their "shining star".
OL,11,FHe said: "We will be forever proud of
OL,12,Fhim and he leaves a void in our lives
OL,13,Fwhich will never be filled."
